y falling than predicted. The kinematic\ndistributions and multiplicities of jets are adequately modeled by certain\ncombinations of next-to-leading-order calculations and parton shower models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Mar 2018 16:02:37 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 18 Jun 2018 14:12:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-06-20"}
