ent. Our theory, moreover, predicts that the reservoir occupation is\nclamped at a constant value whenever the system hosts an odd number of Bose\ncondensates.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 23 Mar 2018 16:24:31 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-04"}
